{"tid":1448554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:08.000Z","uid":118665,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3d083f94b1c798ea938ad35a136b198c8bf8e6","tid":1448554,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=3a4a30d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e171dd9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"835f233523da84dcd4afef61129d8fb549131839","tid":1448554,"uid":281720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f33253fb5e8335c3221667002bfbb9d95f52d9","tid":1448554,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c87d945ba8b44fcdf9a43fc7c7dbe4d8955b0f0","tid":1448554,"uid":14896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95bd46585e2233166e4f2116e2b60797a5d97296","tid":1448554,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB